label: Disable Super Operators
detail: Disables the generation of super operators; this fixes some of the problems when using the obfuscator, but may decrease the performance of your script.

label: Maximum Security Enabled
detail: Enables Max Security to prevent deobfuscation and avoid hooking the Equality Opcode.

label: Encrypt All Strings
detail: Encrypt All Strings encrypts every string that is being obfuscated by PSU Obfuscator. May decrease performance drastically.

label: Enhanced Output
detail: Enables "Enhanced Output"; this will make your file size very larger and can affect performance.

label: Premium Format
detail: This uses a more complex script structure. This is best paired with PSU_MAX_SECURITY Macro.
